The '''''Salamander''''' was an [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B]] [[Frigate/Legends|escort frigate]] that served with the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|Defense Fleet]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The vessel was dispatched to the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Krann]] in order to investigate a threat on the [[Nova crystal/Legends|nova crystal]] [[Mining/Legends|mines]] located there.

